495
00:30:18,716 --> 00:30:19,516
Shut up!

496
00:30:20,917 --> 00:30:21,556
Get out of here!

497
00:30:21,796 --> 00:30:22,917
Get out immediately!

498
00:30:23,157 --> 00:30:24,076
Get out of the company!

499
00:30:24,316 --> 00:30:25,516
Get out of the An family!

500
00:30:40,157 --> 00:30:41,117
