the atmosphere right♪

569
00:35:00,800 --> 00:35:05,472
♪Not falling into a deadlock♪

570
00:35:07,584 --> 00:35:09,760
♪The stubbornness at a certain moment♪

571
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:11,872
♪I let go of my reason♪

572
00:35:11,872 --> 00:35:14,080
♪Repeatedly wanting to try♪

573
00:35:14,080 --> 00:35:16,384
♪To retain and to restrain♪

574
00:35:16,384 --> 00:35:18,560
♪Pass through my world♪

575
00:35:18,560 --> 00:35:22,048
♪Disrupt the established order♪

576
00:35:23,264 --> 00:35:25,792
♪Prove it time and again♪

577
00:35:25,792 --> 00:35:28,448
♪I loved you, that's a fact♪

578
00:35:28,448 --> 00:35:29,824
♪The truer the outcome♪

579
00:35:29,824 --> 00:35:33,152
♪The more endless the failed attempts♪

580
00:35:33,152 --> 00:35:36,224
♪How is there stillness between us♪

581
00:35:36,224 --> 00:35:40,960
♪Desire to uncover further issues♪

582
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:43,072
♪Approaching your inner thoughts♪

583
00:35:43,072 --> 00:35:46,624
♪I only see your own shadow♪

584
00:35:46,624 --> 00:35:48,544
♪Perhaps I'm immature♪

585
00:35:48,544 --> 00:35:51,104
♪Perhaps I'm too presumptuous♪

586
00:35:51,104 --> 00:35:53,536
♪Keep still from now on♪

587
00:35:53,536 --> 00:35:58,176
♪Stay in the original place, both of us♪

588
00:36:50,237 --> 00:36:52,156
I know this is hard for you.

589
00:36:52,636 --> 00:36:54,076
